{"tid":1745241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報 : 香港享有比歷史上任何時候都廣泛的民主","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T22:39:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f74fe5c2a7d4f00a0fea1d8ac6e9b1046699c9a8","tid":1745241,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:22:56.000Z","msg":"人民日報海外版發表專欄文章，批評美國國會不顧中國政府多次強烈反對，通過《香港人權與民主法案》，如果美方一意孤行，中方必將採取有力措施予以反制，一切後果由美方完全承擔。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，法案內容顛倒黑白、混淆視聽，絲毫站不住腳，批評美國政客無資格對一個自由度及法治排名都高於自己的別國地區，指手畫腳，強調香港回歸以來，一國兩制實踐取得舉世公認的成功，香港作為國際金融、航運、貿易中心的地位不斷鞏固，香港同胞享有比歷史上任何時候都廣泛的民主權利與自由。<br />\n<br />\n文章再次要求美方立即停止插手香港事務、干涉中國內政，認清大勢、懸崖勒馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493781-20191122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493781-20191122.htm&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=43ce2fc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493781-20191122.htm&h=a651260d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493781-20191122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dd67cee3c3c7c935a3211a16a6e2664eeb325604","tid":1745241,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"美國人拒絕懸崖勒馬, 中国人非常不高興"},{"pid":"9e9ef7b832f016b979f96d39123531471aaf0b84","tid":1745241,"uid":218313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"具社會主義特式的香港民煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd91bb69c8d05cfd03ab1d741d1ba916359c99e","tid":1745241,"uid":196696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:25:48.000Z","msg":"難道法治程度仲低過美國既中國就可以對法院指手劃腳?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6c01b7ca0d6ee30d85f92aa32cc28a1bb1ee66","tid":1745241,"