{"pid":"485bfb66fc6cb7321e4be8ed045d024a913b4380","tid":1745241,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"做黑狗咪有自由，鐘意拉就拉，打就打，姦就姦，一般市民就連著衫嘅自由都無，後生著黑衫即拉"},{"pid":"7c8a6d59c2da7126f09ea309b953d144742db9b1","tid":1745241,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=76fa4957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abdbad77a0acc2a9b371145d89815fab0fd6bd78","tid":1745241,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"大陸講嘅民主係人民民主專政<br />\n雖然我都唔知點解呢幾隻字可以擺埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8182267446e608f15f95a8e4d6f08180e93b35","tid":1745241,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"